column5: So many fish in the boat today my arms are sore.  Here's a few pics off my cell, girlfriend has all the better ones on her digital camera.  one of many double headers  big fish of the day
AWESOME  Are you keeping and eating?
Boy you've done well and timed it right.  We were there this time of year 2 yrs ago.  Strong north winds the whole time.  Nobody went out.  So disappointed......excuse to go back
we've kept a half dozen snapper and one sea trout mostly c& r.  I can defiantly recommend a great backcountry guide
Nice! You should've kept a snook though, they taste great!
